2025.09.01. Modified rkglPointCloudNormal and rkglOctreeNormal not to specify line widths in the function. [rkgl_shape]
2025.09.01. Modified rkglPointCloud, rkglPointCloudNormal, and rkglOctreeNormal not to set color in the function. [rkgl_shape]
2025.05.12. Renamed members near and far of rkglCamera to znear and zfar, respectively, in order to avoid conflicts in MS Visual C++ (thanks to Daishi Kaneta). [rkgl_camera]
2025.05.11. Removed register qualifiers from terra_smooth_test.c. [example]
